class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Application\\Handler\\ExecuteLlmStepWorker"
type: readonly final class
summary: This class serves as a message handler for executing LLM steps within the agent execution domain. It coordinates with the platform to perform the step logic and dispatches the resulting state updates via a dedicated command bus.
